item.title: CVE-2021-24784|2024-08-03T19:42:17.198Z -- unknown -- wp%20admin%20logo%20changer
item.description: The WP Admin Logo Changer WordPress plugin through 1.0 does not have CSRF check when saving its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin update them via a CSRF attack.
